channel.title: Wor v3
channel.description:
Well I'm done coding Private servers so this will be my last release yes I am moparwha but I forgot my password so I made this account. This is basically the same thing as RZPK or RZSCAPE This is
WORLD OF RZ
I was planning to make it more of a hard training, dedicated server, but I just made it like a pking server.
Yes this is a VERY CRAPPY SERVER AND A LOT MUST BE DONE TO IT But I this was the only time I wanted to release it and I didn't want to waste time working on it.
Other than fixing a few bugs its a good source.
I'll give credits to anyone who tutorials I used.
A lot of things aren't finished either.
What it has Green=Finished Red=Unfinished But it has it
Grand Exchange (See below) Quests (Delta because I didn't want to remove) Prayers Teleports All of them real except 2 that teleport you to Edge and Falador. Same Falador home Barrows Pest Control Castle Wars Dueling at duel arena(JUST ABOUT FINISHED)
Much more but I'm to lazy to type them.
